  "Remembered": [
    { "type": "text", "content": "Ah, {player_name}......." },
    { "type": "text", "content": "So you remembered." },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "The experiments were a success."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "But what were they even for?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Our purpose is given to us by the society we're born into."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "As well as the way we see the world."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "We aren't born with an innate world view. It's given to us."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "And dispelling this illusion gives us a sort of freedom."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "A freedom to decide our own world view."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "To look at the world with fresh eyes."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Anyway, we are about to start another cycle."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Continuing now will bring you back to where you began."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "And onwards into an endless loop."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Until next time......"
    }
  ],
  "Outro": [
    { "type": "text", "content": "Here's all that you need to know." },
    { "type": "text", "content": "We'll be running a series of experiments." },
    { "type": "text", "content": "This will take place on a desert island." },
    {
      "type": "text",
